along with the data
before and after the changes.

00:23:02.950 --> 00:23:04.510
Cross-reference them, and you'll find out

00:23:04.510 --> 00:23:07.390
who really caused 50,000 players
to get free characters.

00:23:07.390 --> 00:23:08.290
Lu Junxi!

