Stellaris might be the best company
in the industry.

00:24:02.820 --> 00:24:03.560
But

00:24:04.060 --> 00:24:06.260
I want to find the one that suits me best.

00:24:09.000 --> 00:24:10.100
Just like dating.

00:24:11.530 --> 00:24:13.730
